name: The Doctor is calling
description: I was passing by this Pharmacy on a Tram while being "high" on CBD the other day. CBD (with less than 1% of THC) is legal in Switzerland since 2016, the Doctors and Pharmacies are seeing the good effects for some people nowadays as well. What a time to be alive! Shot by me in Zurich at Kreutzplatz, Zurich in Ocotber 2021 / 3024×4032 pixels / 8.5 MB / JPEG
